'''TrES-2b'''或稱'''克卜勒1b'''（'''Kepler-1b'''），是一個環繞著[[天龍座|天龍座]]恆星[[GSC_03549-02811|GSC 03549-02811]]（TrES-2）的[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]，距太陽系750光年。TrES-2b於2011年被確認是表面最暗的系外行星，它的[[反照率|反照率]]小於1%<ref name=darkest>{{cite journal | url = http://mnrasl.oxfordjournals.org/content/417/1/L88 | author = David M. Kipping & David S. Spiegel | title = Detection of visible light from the darkest world | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | accessdate = 2011-08-12 | archive-date = 2020-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200315192737/https://academic.oup.com/mnrasl/article/417/1/L88/1039066 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該行星的質量和半徑代表它是組成成分類似木星的[[類木行星|類木行星]]，但它極為靠近母恆星，因此是典型的[[熱木星|熱木星]]。本行星系位於[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]的[[視野|視野]]中<ref name=disco>{{cite journal | url=http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1538-4357/651/1/L61/21047.html | title=TrES-2: The First Transiting Planet in the Kepler Field | journal=[[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] Letters | volume=651 | year=2006 | pages=L61–L64 | doi=10.1086/509123 | bibcode=2006ApJ...651L..61O|arxiv = astro-ph/0609335 | issue=1 |last1=O'Donovan|first1=Francis T. | last2=Charbonneau | first2=David | last3=Mandushev | first3=Georgi | last4=Dunham | first4=Edward W. | last5=Latham | first5=David W. | last6=Torres | first6=Guillermo | last7=Sozzetti | first7=Alessandro | last8=Brown | first8=Timothy M. | last9=Trauger | first9=John T.}}</ref>。

